  "status": "active",
  "version": 1,
  "summary": "Email body fixed 600px centered; 480px breakpoint collapsing columns; 12-col grid with 1/2/40-60%; 24px side padding; 8px vertical rhythm; 32px vertical padding per section; spacing: heading-body 16px, para-para 16px, body-CTA 24px, img-caption 8px; Brand Blue #00529b primary CTA pill 16px Nunito Sans Bold with 14x32px padding, min 48px height; secondary reversed style; max 1 primary CTA per section; no row alteration."
